{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So again, there was the idea of opening a tent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was given again in the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], what they call [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], which was the admitting office, because they were in different languages-- they were Russian and Polish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted people who are coming one after the other from the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not equipped to give them help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a huge gym where there was nothing, just four huge walls and a tent, I think not even a roof, the sick, injured very heavily people, probably without legs, they came.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all I could do, I couldn't give them a drop of water because we didn't have water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were battle casualties which had-- there was a unit, a field unit, which bandaged them a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they couldn't keep it there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The casualties were very heavy, and they were coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were sending us to us, because at that time we were the closest to the line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not supposed to, but there was nobody else, so they told us go, go go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is-- this was the function which was given to us by the Russian military, who was nearby.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, a few Russian doctors who were equipped and who had the knew-how-- the know-how how to do amputations or how to give more thorough, let's say, surgical treatments, they came and helped in our town-- in the not town, in the tent, which was open, which was our surgical room.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was predominantly in that admitting office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And over 24 hours, I didn't close my eye.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The people were coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had to take their papers to register them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took their knapsack and put it under their head.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
